prompts.frontCover: A whimsical and charming watercolor painting of a slightly frazzled, but very happy, cartoon sloth wearing a tiny, lopsided party hat, clinging precariously to a single, brightly colored birthday balloon that is slowly floating upwards. The sloth has a goofy, contented grin. Below the sloth, the words "happy belated birthday...ish" are written in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is set against a clean, off-white background with a visible paper texture. The watercolor style is evident with soft, blended colors, artistic paint splatters in festive hues (like teal, magenta, and sunny yellow) around the edges, and organic paint bleeds, giving it a handcrafted, flat 2D feel.
